# Setting Up a Virtual Environment for Python Dependencies

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
```

## Step 2: Activate the Virtual Environment

On Mac

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
```

On Windows
```bash
.venv\Scripts\activate
```

## Step 3: Install Required Packages

```bash
pip install requests
```

## Step 4: Run Script

```bash
python script.py
```